      <title>尼日利亚货币的惊人涨幅尚未抑制通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/-usd-ngn-nigerian-currency-s-world-beating-gains-yet-to-temper-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚通货膨胀率超出预期，达到 28 年来的新高，因为该国货币的飙升尚未反映进口商品的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/-usd-ngn-nigerian-currency-s-world-beating-gains-yet-to-temper-inflation</guid>
