    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击前看涨石油期权交易以创纪录的速度增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/bullish-oil-options-traded-at-record-pace-before-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊朗对以色列发动攻击前几天，石油投资者纷纷涌入期权市场，并交易了创纪录数量的合约，从价格上涨中获利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/bullish-oil-options-traded-at-record-pace-before-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度季风降雨充沛将促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度预测今年的季风将高于正常水平，人们乐观地认为充足的降雨将刺激农作物产量和经济增长，并促使政府放松对小麦、大米和食糖出口的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度3月份贸易逆差收窄至11个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-march-trade-gap-narrows-to-11-month-low-on-low-import-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度3月份的贸易逆差收窄至11个月低点，原因是该国控制了进口费用，而全球需求的复苏有助于保持出口稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-march-trade-gap-narrows-to-11-month-low-on-low-import-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于避险买盘减弱，通胀担忧让债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末前席卷市场的国债买盘正在平息，人们希望伊朗和以色列之间的冲突现在能够平息，人们的注意力又回到了困扰世界经济的通胀压力上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/treasuries-haven-role-faces-pressure-from-oil-price-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
